        <p>The Renter will be able to (i) book the trip to start at any time of the day subject to availability; and (ii) choose a start time of the trip from the next hour from the time of the booking.</p>
        <br>
        <p>Upon receipt of booking request in relation to a vehicle, Drive2Co shall confirm such booking and communicate details of the final booking with the Host and the Renter through an email, text message or message via the Platform confirming such booking.</p>
        <br>
        <p>By accepting these terms relating to the online booking process, the parties hereby acknowledge and agree that (i) each of the Host and Renter accept the conditions for listing the vehicle on the Drive2Co Platform and use of Drive2Co Services, (ii) Drive2Co is merely a facilitator and any arrangements entered into between Host and Renter through this Platform or otherwise is solely at their’ own risk and expense.</p>
